channel.title: [2006] Stonedscape [2006] NOT A REMAKE!
channel.description:
[b][size=24pt]FIRST OFF THIS IS NOT A REMAKE! AND NEVER WILL BE! THIS IS ALSO DELTA AND WILL ALWAYS BE DELTA![/size]
Stonedscape is a old 2006 based server! We will be adding most skill if all, Also quest/events We need some extra, help with this as we want weekly updates! This project was started on 10/4/12 and have been working hard ever since! You can apply for GfX developer, server developer, client developer, or web developer!
[size=10pt]*What made want to do this? *Lostmyphat kinda talked me into it. *What do i plan on doing with this? *Making an old school server that you cant really find these days. *To make this i will need a few server and client dev. *If you would like to help let me know![/size] [img]http://i45.tinypic.com/f08z8x.png[/img] [img]http://i45.tinypic.com/1ghh93.png[/img] [b]All credits go to lostmyphat atm for this clean source![/b]
